{"tid":1950224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[CCTVB]今晚唔知幾點「機場特警」，推到完場","createTime":"2020-03-30T07:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T15:45:55.000Z","uid":1834,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09203648e9bc61808058aad1687d3569bb99e38a","tid":1950224,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20170322/56465497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170322%2F56465497&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=82d421ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170322%2F56465497&h=678fdb53\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20170322/56465497</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>23/3/2017</strong><br />\n消防總隊目<strong>邱少明</strong>為拯救行山被困的男女而失足墮崖殉職，該對男女最終被消防員成功救出，送院敷治後已無礙出院。《蘋果》獲悉，該對男女原來是在機場工作的情侶，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">32歲姓溫的男子是機場特警</span></strong></span>，30歲姓劉的女子則是機場保安女隊長，兩人雖逃過大難，但消防員卻喪命，事件在機場同事的圈子中引起很大的震憾。<br />\n<br />\n救護車於昨午4時40分，把該對一度迷路被困的行山男女送抵威院治理，32歲姓溫的男子左手受傷但已即場包紮，他傷勢較輕，可自行從救護車下車及坐上輪椅送進急症室；30歲姓劉的女子則頭部及下巴受傷，需以繃帶包紮及披上保暖毯，以擔架床送院。消息稱，獲救男女送院後得悉事件中有消防員殉職，據悉兩人均感難過和自責。記者昨曾致電溫氏，但他拒作回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人在此向已故消防總隊目邱少明先生致敬,並強烈譴責TVB播出有關「機場特警」提材對已故消防總隊目邱少明先生遺屬作二次傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人唔會忘記</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503e4f0e62511074bffc052cee9452e5ec9cfc57","tid":1950224,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/166913/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/166913/</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b872e2cf82e3e4a0e45ae2e77e9014384c47f18f","t